					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a tale that I've been meaning to write for a while ever since someone pointed out to me that Rebecca Soss seemed like an ideal candidate for SCP-4999. It didn't make sense to me to write about Rebecca's final moments in life as much as it made sense to write about the last piece of evidence that she was alive.</p> <p><strong>Valued Critters:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/basicskipreader" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6657366&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596093279" alt="basicskipreader" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6657366)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/basicskipreader" >basicskipreader</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596093279" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span></p> <hr /> <p>Was this something you liked? I've written <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rtme-author">a lot of stuff</a>.</p> <hr /> <p>I also suggest the following:</p> <p><strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4999">SCP-4999</a> &#8212; Someone to Watch Over Us</strong><br /> <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3881">SCP-3881</a> &#8212; A Disregarded Proposal</strong><br /> <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3511">SCP-3511</a> &#8212; Reach Out And Touch</strong><br /> <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/robin">Robin</a>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596093279" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></strong></p> <p>And thank you for reading.</p> 
				 	]]>
